metadata.name: My MEGAMI Vie
metadata.description:
This artwork is fan art for the MEGAMI project using #megamiathome.

Vie is a gamer. He can be angry and gets a little violent when he doesn't win a game. It looks like she broke her precious controller.

This artwork complies with the MEGAMI Art License.
Respect and gratitude to Naoki Saito-sensei and the MEGAMI Project!
